Title: The Body Care Diamond Shimmer Bleach(100 g)
Description: Diamond shimmer bleach - the body care diamond shimmer bleach cream is a unique bleach cream that blends facial hair, cleanses skin pores, removes impurities and fades facial blemishes from deep within making you glow with a dazzling shine.the therapeutic advantage of diamond with the highest standard of modern technology is the secret of the dazzling new. Body care diamond shimmer bleach cream provides extra active oxygen that penetrates into your skin and nourishes it. Diamond shimmer bleach helps lightens it to match the skin color and make the skin fairer and glowing. Its mild formula gives more texture without causing any irritation to skin at all. Key benefits : cleanses the dead skin, giving a fresh, clear skin no skin irritation helps lightens blemishes, pigmentation and dark patches cleanses the dead skin, giving a fresh, clear skin regulates excess oil secretion reaffirming, tightening and uplifting actions cools & soothes the skin long lasting firmness and resilience cleans clogged pores gives a fresh, glowing ,clear and soft skin improves complexion cream ingredients light liquid paraffine, emulsifying wax, glycerin, citric acid, hydrogen peroxide, dm water, active diamond, activator ingredient sammonium bicarbonate, silica struction for use : wash area to be bleach with cold water and pat dry.take out 2 spatulas of cream on the tray. Add 2 pinches of powder activator on the cream. The weight proportion is approximately 6g of cream bleach to 1 g of powder activator. Maintain this proportion for .larger or smaller quantities of bleach needed. Close the powder activator bottle immediately after taking. Mix the cream bleach and powder activator for 2 minutes till the powder completely dissolves.apply the mixture on the desired area. Covering all hair to be bleached. Avoid application on eyebrows and around the eyes. Leave it for 15-20 minutes. For darker skin, allow the application of bleach for 10 minutes only. Wash off with cold water. Do not use soap for 3 hours after bleach. Precaution : before using this product, patch test should be carried out.

Title: Ralph Lauren Polo Explorer EDT  -  125 ml
Description: Refreshing and sensual, Polo Explorer from the house of Ralph Lauren, is an Eau de Toilette that enthralls the senses with its gourmand aroma. Enticing woody and aromatic notes are inter-mingled in the luxurious Polo Explorer by perfumers Honorine Blanc and Harry Fremont, to create an invigorating scent for a mysterious, daring man who likes adventure. Opening with a fresh top note of mandarin and bergamot, Polo Explorer trails into a heart of coriander and warm leather accords. A base note of fragrant sandalwood, mahogany and ambrosial accords lends a subtle hint of masculine sensuality to this heady aroma. Powerful and intoxicating, Polo Explorer is reminiscent of lush equatorial forests, of uncharted territory and emblematic of the man who remains undaunted by it all.

Title: Issey Miyake L'Eau D'Issey Summer Eau de Toilette  -  125 ml(For Men)
Description: Issey Miyake is a fashion brand which was founded in Japan in 1970 by Issey Miyake---a rather complicated name for Europeans. He was born in 1938 in the unlucky city of Hiroshima where at the age of seven, he witnessed and survived the explosion of the atomic bomb. Young Issey Miyake was remarkable mainly for his sense of design and fabric research. Not afraid to go against traditional fashion norms, Miyake’s unconventional methods proved successful and eventually led to him entering the world of perfumes in 1992. With complicated perfume names, Miyake targets women by complimenting Japanese tradition, culture, and nature. Try fragrances like his mysterious Issey Miyake L’Eau D’Issey Blue Por Homme or one of his classics Issey Miyake L’Eau D’Issey.

The fragrance opens on a heady wave of incense, almost as if to forewarn: incense is the quintessential perfume of Mediterranean and Middle Eastern lands, intoxicating, permeating and seducing, with no hesitations. A call to action heralding the rich smoky tones of the dark wood and mysterious deep ambery notes that follow. Perception dissolves in the final celebration of the soft musky notes, leaving the hot, heady aroma of a successful conquest lingering on the skin.
